==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hypochondria
<hw>Hy`po*chon"dri*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL.]</ety>
<fld>(Med.)</fld> <def>An excessive concern about one's own health,
particularly a morbid worry about illnesses which a person imagines are
affecting him, often focusing on specific symptoms; also called
<altname>hypochondriasis</altname>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hypochondriac</ent>⟦br⟧
